20 Section 1111. A. Rape is an act of sexual intercourse
21 involving vaginal or anal penetration accomplished with a male or
22 female within or without the bonds of matrimony who may be of the
23 same or the opposite sex as the perpetrator under any of the
24 following circumstances:
