8 SECTION 2. AMENDATORY 21 O.S. 2021, Section 1112, is
9 amended to read as follows:
10 Section 1112. No person can be convicted of rape or rape by
11 instrumentation on account of an act of sexual intercourse with
12 anyone over the age of fourteen (14) years and under the age of
13 eighteen (18) years, with his or her consent, unless such person was
14 over the age of eighteen (18) years more than four (4) years older
15 than the other person at the time of such act.
